not so much for the play

512
00:29:27,349 --> 00:29:29,602
but for the handsome
young bachelors in the crowd.

513
00:29:29,685 --> 00:29:31,145
We can practise
our flirtations.

514
00:29:31,228 --> 00:29:33,355
I should like to go
because I should like to go.

515
00:29:33,439 --> 00:29:34,982
