527
00:30:17,316 --> 00:30:20,653
-Uh, you look very...
-No, thank you. So do you.

528
00:30:20,736 --> 00:30:22,321
-Thank you.
-Thank you. Shall we...

529
00:30:22,404 --> 00:30:25,574
-Yes, let’s...
-Yes, let’s sit down. Good.

530
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:28,452
