00:30:49,431 --> 00:30:51,350
Boatswain!

536
00:30:52,726 --> 00:30:55,479
Here, master!
What cheer?

537
00:30:55,563 --> 00:30:58,357
Good, speak
to the mariners.

538
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:02,820
Fall to’t, yarely,
or we run ourselves aground:

539
00:31:02,903 --> 00:31:06,740
bestir, bestir.

