looked in your journal.

562
00:32:26,362 --> 00:32:27,946
Well, that... that was nosy.

563
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:29,531
I’m afraid it’s one
of my many flaws.

564
00:32:29,615 --> 00:32:31,784
-Nosiness?
-I’m very nosy, yes.

565
00:32:31,867 --> 00:32:34,370
